INSTALLATION

    To install this module, run the following commands:

        perl Makefile.PL
        make
        make test
        make install

    Alternatively, to install with Module::Build, you can use the
    following commands:

        perl Build.PL
        ./Build
        ./Build test
        ./Build install


SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

    After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
    perldoc command.

        perldoc PerlIO::via::escape_ansi

    You can also look for information at:

        RT, CPAN's request tracker
            http://rt.cpan.org/Dist/Display.html?Queue=PerlIO-via-escape_ansi

        AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
            http://annocpan.org/dist/PerlIO-via-escape_ansi

        CPAN Ratings
            http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/PerlIO-via-escape_ansi

        Search CPAN
            http://search.cpan.org/dist/PerlIO-via-escape_ansi


